reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft and Pretty
reviews.reviewText: I love how this ornament looks. The flowers do come squished, but they're easy to shape open, and they stay that way. The yarn is nice and soft too. The flowers can be removed since the are held in place by a knot that is inserted into the little hole at the top of the flower. This would be nice for just cleaning a single flower and then putting it back on.I made a simple modification in order to get them to look a bit more like lily of the valley flowers. I just trimmed off the two that hung off the main strand, separated them, then tied them back onto it at different points for the cascading effect. This will make it trickier to remove/install on the mirror, but I plan to keep them on there. Anyway, it's why my picture looks a little different than the product photo.
